# 🤖 FormSaarthi AI Extension

AI-powered Chrome Extension that assists users while filling scholarship and government forms.

---

## 🚀 Features (Current)

- ✅ Chrome Extension (Manifest V3)
- ✅ React + Vite
- ✅ CRXJS Setup
- ✅ Floating AI Button
- ✅ Sliding Sidebar
- 🔄 AI Chat (In Progress)
- 🔄 Form Field Detection (Planned)
- 🔄 OCR & Autofill (Planned)

---

# 📦 Tech Stack

- React
- Vite
- CRXJS
- Chrome Extension Manifest V3
- React Icons
- Axios

---

# 🛠 Prerequisites

Install:

- Node.js (LTS)
- Git
- Google Chrome

---

# 📥 Installation

Clone the repository

```bash
git clone <repo-url>
```

Go inside the extension

```bash
cd hackathon_project
```

Install dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

---

# ▶️ Development

Run

```bash
npm run build
```

---

# 📂 Load Extension

Open Chrome

```
chrome://extensions
```

Enable

```
Developer Mode
```

Click

```
Load unpacked
```

Select

```
formsaarthi-ai/dist
```

---

# 🔄 Development Workflow

Whenever you make changes

```text
Edit Code
        ↓
npm run build
        ↓
Reload Extension
        ↓
Refresh Website
```

> **Note:** Chrome does not automatically reload unpacked extensions after a build.

