# 👥 Team Workflow

Create a separate branch before working.

```bash
git checkout -b feature-name
```

Examples

```
feature/sidebar

feature/chat

feature/ocr

feature/backend
```

After completing a feature

```bash
git add .

git commit -m "Added Sidebar"

git push
```

Create a Pull Request before merging into `main`.

